Library Management System

All data must be stored in memory and entered from the console.

Add book
Remove book
Show all books
Sort books
Search book
Book analytics
Exit

1. Add Book
Read all book information from the console.
id must be unique.
If a book with the same id already exists, display an error message.

2. Remove Book
Remove a book by id.
If the book does not exist, display an appropriate message.

3. Show All Books
Display all books in a readable format.
The order is not important.

4. Sort Books (Ask the user which field to sort by)
By title (ASC)
By publication year (DESC)
By author, then by title (ASC)
By price (ASC)

5. Search Book (Streams REQUIRED)
Search by id
Search by title (partial match)
Search by author (partial match)

6. Book Analytics (Streams ONLY) (Optional)
Calculate the average book price.
Find the most expensive book.
Find the 3 newest books.
Count books by author.
Count books by category.

  Bu tapşırıq Employee Management System ilə eyni çətinlik səviyyəsindədir və
  ArrayList, Comparator, Stream API, filter, sorted, max, average, limit, collect və
  digər Java mövzularını işlətmək üçün uyğundur.